      "fengsheng": {
        "content": [
          {
            "verse": "isa.59.21",
            "paragraphs": [
              "59:21",
              "我……的靈……的話：神應許要將聖靈加給那些轉離罪和接受救主的人(比較約16:13；徒2:4)，他的話語也必不再離開他們的口。神的靈和神的話語將永遠堅固真教會的見證和會眾直到永遠。神子民必須在聖靈的能力和公義中傳講福音(參徒1:8註；參“聖靈浸”一文)。"
            ]
          }
        ],
        "title": "豐盛生命研讀本"
      },
      "leili": {
        "content": [
          {
            "verse": "isa.59.17-21",
            "paragraphs": [
              "五九17～21基督再來的時候，祂將要審判仇敵（17～19節），給以色列帶來拯救（20,21節；比較羅一一26,27）。\"救贖主\"一詞（20節）是指近親買贖者（參看得三9的腳註）；即與祂所救贖的人有親屬的關系，這指出了道成肉身的必須（來二14～16）。這裏的\"約\"是指新約。參看耶利米書三十一章31至34節的腳註。",
              "──《雷歷研讀本聖經》"
            ]
          }
        ],
        "title": "雷厲研讀本聖經",
        "author": "雷厲"
      }
    },
    "versions": {
      "ccb": {
        "version_id": "CCB",
        "version_name": "圣经当代译本",
        "lang": "chs",
        "text": "耶和华说：“我亲自与他们立约，我赐给他们的灵和我放在他们口中的话，必不离开他们和他们的子子孙孙，从现在直到永远。这是耶和华说的。”"
      },
      "cnv": {
        "version_id": "CNV",
        "version_name": "新譯本",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "耶和華說：“至於我，我與他們所立的約是這樣：我加在你們身上的靈和我放在你口裡的話，必不離開你的口，不離開你後裔的口，也不離開你後裔的後裔的口，從現在直到永遠；這是耶和華說的。”"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "耶和華說：「至於我與他們所立的約乃是這樣：我加給你的靈，傳給你的話，必不離你的口，也不離你後裔與你後裔之後裔的口，從今直到永遠；這是耶和華說的。」"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "“As for Me, this is My covenant with them,” says the Lord: “My Spirit which is upon you, and My words which I have put in your mouth shall not depart from your mouth, nor from the mouth of your offspring, nor from the mouth of your offspring’s offspring,” says the Lord, “from now and forever.”"
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "“As for me, this is my covenant with them,” says the Lord. “My Spirit, who is on you, will not depart from you, and my words that I have put in your mouth will always be on your lips, on the lips of your children and on the lips of their descendants—from this time on and forever,” says the Lord."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "“And this is my covenant with them,” says the Lord. “My Spirit will not leave them, and neither will these words I have given you. They will be on your lips and on the lips of your children and your children’s children forever. I, the Lord, have spoken!"
      }
    },
